name: MyParkSaversNews
0:
”Alexa, open Park Savers News”
”Alexa, ask Park Savers News for the latest update”
”Alexa, start Park Savers News”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: park savers news
des: Love staying up to date on Disney theme park news? The Park Savers blog has come to Amazon Alexa to share up-to-the-minute news, keeping you informed of new park additions, openings, park changes, attraction updates, reviews and more. Enjoy your news with daily updates by asking Alexa to "load My Park Savers News." You'll be told the latest theme park news and even enjoy a fun fact or two!
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
